Copies of original document defining the constitution or legal status, place of registration and principal place of business of the company or firm or partnership entity.

The bidder should have completed projects of similar nature (ACP Board Cladding, LED Acrylic Letter/Letter Board, Embedded Acrylic LED Board, Channel Letters, Stainless Steel Letter Signboard, Acrylic Display Board, Flange Sign Board, Outdoor Advertisement, Prefabrication work etc.) of value Rs.5 (Five) crores during the last three financial years.

Details of the experience and past performance of the bidder on works of similar nature within the last three financial years, and details of current work in hand and other Contractual commitments shall be submitted as per Annexure IV Schedule 1 and Schedule II of this bidding document.
The bidder should enclose a copy of PAN and GST Certificate along with the tender documents.

The bidder should enclose the original demand draft for cost of tender as well as EMD drawn in favor of Bihar State Milk Co-operative Federation Ltd. payable at Patna along with the technical bid or through payment gateway provided by e-procurement portal www.eproc2.bihar.gov.in
The bidder should enclose an undertaking with regards to non-black listing by any Govt or Semi-Govt or PSU or Cooperative institutions.

The average annual turnover of the bidder should be Rs.8 (Eight) Crores during the last three financial years. The bidder is required to submit the CA?s certificate and Profit & Loss and Balance Sheet for the last three financial years (2020-21, 2021-22 and 202-23).
